{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":860,"text":"I was born in Taiwan."},{"time":2595,"text":"I grew up surrounded by"},{"time":4419,"text":"different types of hardware stores,"},{"time":7119,"text":"and I like going to night markets."},{"time":9467,"text":"I love the energy of the night markets,"},{"time":11307,"text":"the colors, the lights, the toys,"},{"time":13859,"text":"and all the unexpected things I find every time I go,"},{"time":17302,"text":"things like watermelon with straw antennas"},{"time":20672,"text":"or puppies with mohawks."},{"time":24494,"text":"When I was growing up, I liked taking toys apart,"},{"time":27304,"text":"any kind of toys I'd find around the house,"},{"time":29328,"text":"like my brother's BB gun when he's not home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":31562,"text":"I also liked to make environments"},{"time":33580,"text":"for people to explore and play."},{"time":35668,"text":"In these early installations,"},{"time":37618,"text":"I would take plastic sheets, plastic bags,"},{"time":40146,"text":"and things I would find in the hardware store"},{"time":41986,"text":"or around the house."},{"time":43202,"text":"I would take things like highlighter pen,"},{"time":45938,"text":"mix it with water, pump it through plastic tubing,"},{"time":49390,"text":"creating these glowing circulatory systems"},{"time":51902,"text":"for people to walk through and enjoy."},{"time":54286,"text":"I like these materials because of the way they look,"},{"time":56794,"text":"the way they feel, and they're very affordable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60090,"text":"I also liked to make devices\nthat work with body parts."},{"time":62916,"text":"I would take camera LED lights"},{"time":65094,"text":"and a bungee cord and strap it on my waist"},{"time":67235,"text":"and I would videotape my belly button,"},{"time":69394,"text":"get a different perspective,"},{"time":70416,"text":"and see what it does."},{"time":72778,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":74940,"text":"I also like to modify household appliances."},{"time":77522,"text":"This is an automatic night light."},{"time":78820,"text":"Some of you might have them at home."},{"time":80434,"text":"I would cut out the light sensor,"},{"time":82066,"text":"add an extension line,"},{"time":83970,"text":"and use modeling clay,"},{"time":85466,"text":"stick it onto the television,"},{"time":87242,"text":"and then I would videotape my eye,"},{"time":89254,"text":"and using the dark part of my eye"},{"time":91122,"text":"tricking the sensor into thinking it's night time,"},{"time":93002,"text":"so you turn on the lightbulb."},{"time":94754,"text":"The white of the eye and the eyelid"},{"time":96674,"text":"will trick the sensor into thinking it's daytime,"},{"time":98866,"text":"and it will shut off the light."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101632,"text":"I wanted to collect more different types of eyes,"},{"time":103720,"text":"so I built this device using bicycle helmets,"},{"time":106464,"text":"some lightbulbs and television sets."},{"time":108880,"text":"It would be easier for other\npeople to wear the helmet"},{"time":111271,"text":"and record their eyes."},{"time":113596,"text":"This device allows me to symbolically"},{"time":116718,"text":"extract other people's eyes,"},{"time":118262,"text":"so I have a diversity of eyes to use"},{"time":120159,"text":"for my other sculptures."},{"time":128829,"text":"This sculpture has four eyes."},{"time":130589,"text":"Each eye is controlling a different device."},{"time":132757,"text":"This eye is turning itself around in a television."},{"time":136237,"text":"This eye is inflating a plastic tube."},{"time":138653,"text":"This eye is watching a video\nof another piece being made."},{"time":142229,"text":"And these two eyes are activating glowing water."},{"time":146191,"text":"Many of these pieces are later on shown"},{"time":148173,"text":"in museums, biennials, triennial exhibitions"},{"time":150517,"text":"around the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152867,"text":"I love science and biology."},{"time":155230,"text":"In 2007, I was doing a research fellowship"},{"time":157717,"text":"at the Smithsonian Natural History Museum"},{"time":159765,"text":"looking at bioluminous organisms in the oean."},{"time":162573,"text":"I love these creatures. I love the\nway they look, the way they feel."},{"time":165677,"text":"They're soft, they're slimy,"},{"time":168535,"text":"and I was fascinated by the way they use light"},{"time":170725,"text":"in their environment,"},{"time":171950,"text":"either to attract mates, for self-defense,"},{"time":174020,"text":"or to attract food."},{"time":176818,"text":"This research inspired my\nwork in many different ways,"},{"time":179237,"text":"things like movement or different light patterns."},{"time":186184,"text":"So I started gathering a lot of"},{"time":187621,"text":"different types of material in my studio"},{"time":190352,"text":"and just experimenting"},{"time":191547,"text":"and trying this out, trying that out,"},{"time":193371,"text":"and seeing what types of creatures I can come up with."},{"time":195995,"text":"I used a lot of computer cooling fans"},{"time":198259,"text":"and just kind of put them\ntogether and see what happens."},{"time":201755,"text":"This is an 8,000-square-foot installation"},{"time":203955,"text":"composed of many different creatures,"},{"time":205363,"text":"some hanging from the ceiling\nand some resting on the floor."},{"time":208846,"text":"From afar, they look alien-like,"},{"time":210134,"text":"but when you look closer,"},{"time":211802,"text":"they're all made out of black garbage bags"},{"time":213330,"text":"or Tupperware containers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214950,"text":"I'd like to share with you how ordinary things"},{"time":217910,"text":"can become something magical and wondrous."},{"time":234710,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":292879,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":294735,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}